f(2x)+2xf'(2x)
   \frac\d{\d x}\circ x{*}\, (x\mapsto f(2x))  =\frac\d{\d x}(x\mapsto xf(2x))  =x\mapsto f(2x)+2xf'(2x), 
 \begin{align}   x\mapsto\left(\frac\d{\d x}(x\mapsto xf(x))\right)(2x)  &=x\mapsto\left(x\mapsto f(x)+xf'(x)\right)(2x) \\&=x\mapsto f(2x)+2xf'(2x). \end{align} 
